Class RelationshipAnswerItem

    • org.wikirate4j.entitities.RelationshipAnswerItem

  • public class RelationshipAnswerItem
extends java.lang.Object
    The RelationshipAnswerItem Object represents a relationship answer on a relationship metric type. This object is used when we want to add/update a relationship answer on Wikirate
